 Vanguard News Nigeria. - The Kano State Football Association says it has suspended all local competition matches at the Sani Abacha Stadium in Kano, following a decision by its management. July 26, 2019 In "Sports" Kano Pillars Football Club on Sunday defeated visiting FC Taraba of Jalingo 2-1 in a 2014/2015 Nigeria Professional Football League (NPFL) week six match. April 26, 2015 In "Sports" Kano Pillars Football Club beat visiting Katsina United 3-1 on Sunday to earn the maximum points in a week 21 of the Nigeria Professional Football League (NPFL). May 14, 2018 In "Sports"